basic.name: Storm Bolt
basic.shortTooltip: Throw a hammer, stunning and damaging the first enemy hit
basic.fullTooltip: Throw a hammer, dealing 110 (+4% per level) damage to the first enemy hit and Stunning them for 1.25 seconds.  Quest: Hit 25 Heroes with Storm Bolt. Heroes who die within 2.5 seconds of being hit by Storm Bolt count as hitting 3 additional Heroes.  Reward: Storm Bolt pierces to hit an additional target, and Muradin's Basic Attacks reduce the cooldown of Storm Bolt by 1 second.

basic.name: Pinning Shot
basic.shortTooltip: Slow and damage an enemy
basic.fullTooltip: Deal 100 (+4% per level) damage to an enemy and Slow them by 40% for 2.25 seconds.

basic.name: Entangling Roots
basic.shortTooltip: Root and damage Heroes in an area
basic.fullTooltip: Root enemy Heroes in an area for 1.25 seconds, and deal 117 (+4% per level) damage over the duration. Affected area grows over 3 seconds.

heroic.name: Twilight Dream
heroic.fullTooltip: After 0.5 seconds, deal 310 (+4% per level) damage in a large area around Malfurion, Silencing enemies making them unable to use Abilities for 3 seconds.

trait.name: Blinding Wind
trait.fullTooltip: Throw a cloud of wind at the 2 nearest enemies (prioritizing Heroes), dealing 133 (+4% per level) damage. Affected targets are Blinded for 1.5 seconds, causing their Basic Attacks to miss and deal no damage.

mount.name: Polymorph
mount.fullTooltip: Polymorph a target for 1.5 seconds, Slowing their Movement Speed by 25% and Silencing them. Targets are not able to attack while Polymorphed.

hearth.name: Hook
hearth.shortTooltip: Pull the first target hit towards Stitches
hearth.fullTooltip: Pull the first enemy hit towards Stitches and deal 91 (+4% per level) damage.

basic.name: Void Prison
basic.shortTooltip: Time Stop targets in an area
basic.fullTooltip: Slows time in an area to a near standstill, placing allies and enemies in Time Stop for 5 seconds. Zeratul is not affected.

basic.name: Devouring Maw
basic.shortTooltip: Eats enemies in area
basic.fullTooltip: Summon a Devouring Maw that devours enemies for 4 seconds. Devoured enemies cannot fight and take 88 (+4% per level) damage per second.  Usable on Unstoppable enemies.

basic.name: Cocoon
basic.shortTooltip: Wraps enemy in a cocoon
basic.fullTooltip: Wraps target enemy Hero in a cocoon, rendering them unable to act or be targeted for 7 seconds. Allies of the Hero can attack the cocoon to break it and free them early.

heroic.name: Gorge
heroic.fullTooltip: Consume an enemy Hero, trapping them for 4 seconds. When Gorge ends, the enemy Hero takes 274 (+4% per level) damage. The trapped Hero cannot move or act and doesn't take damage from other sources.

trait.name: Lamb to the Slaughter
trait.shortTooltip: Chain an enemy Hero to a post
trait.fullTooltip: Throw a hitching post that attaches to the nearest enemy Hero after a 1 second delay. This deals 171 (+4% per level) damage and causes the enemy to be chained to the post and Silenced for 3 seconds.

mount.name: Horrify
mount.fullTooltip: After 0.5 seconds, deal 120 (+4% per level) damage to enemy Heroes in an area and Fear them for 2 seconds. While Feared, Heroes are Silenced and are forced to run away from Horrify's center.

hearth.name: Taunt
hearth.shortTooltip: Gain HealthForce a Hero to attack Varian
hearth.fullTooltip: Silence a target Hero and force them to attack Varian for 1.25 seconds.  Passive: Maximum Health and Health Regeneration increased by 30%.
